{"tid":761074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我最喜歡的國歌 top10","createTime":"2018-07-30T05:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T10:52:31.000Z","uid":52068,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8b8255e3a2f4466125bcdbc5341d75dbb0bd8bcd","tid":761074,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:46:03.000Z","msg":"以下全部都係屬於個人喜好，排名主要係根據旋律同埋歌詞決定。歡迎巴打分享自己既意見。<br />\n<br />\n講真，第九第十名真係好難決定，波蘭、墨西哥、德國、葡萄牙、以色列國歌都好好聽。就第十黎講，個人喜好葡萄牙國歌旋律，德國國歌歌詞，係旋律同歌詞既比較下，我選擇左旋律行先，所以個人最鍾意既國歌 top10如下：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10）葡萄牙國歌</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gf3WFGqHM_o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGf3WFGqHM_o&d=GabojfsCkB0Nh5lPrhQ4kgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=dd2f70b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gf3WFGqHM_o</a><br />\n前段節奏一般，但副歌部分激昂振奮，成為葡萄牙國歌能夠擠進頭十的最大&rsquo;&rsquo;功臣&rsquo;&rsquo;。歌詞懷緬祖國為航海霸主，歌頌國家擁有無比的勇氣，來日必定東山再起。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">9）以色列國歌</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bJZpXFCIgbg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbJZpXFCIgbg&d=GabojfsCkB0Nh5lPrhQ4kgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=ca04967e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bJZpXFCIgbg</a><br />\n旋律淒美而又帶點嚴肅莊重，十分獨特。回望歷史，可知猶太民族曾受盡委屈，逼害，因此在歌詞中不難感受到鼓勵民族要堅強的味道，並表達希望終有一天能夠復興自己的民族的意向。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">8）南非國歌</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gr0414FrN7g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGr0414FrN7g&d=GabojfsCkB0Nh5lPrhQ4kgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=5e05b061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gr0414FrN7g</a><br />\n旋律優美、柔和，個人認為南非國歌必定要配上演唱，十分悅耳。歌詞使用五種語言寫成，當中包括英語、南非語和塞索托語等非洲語言，顯示南非是一個民族共融的國家。歌詞內容方面，多為祈求上帝保佑非洲和南非本身，以及南非人民的團結和自由。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">7）國歌</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yNNYTbJD1o&amp;t=71s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0yNNYTbJD1o%26t%3D71s&d=GabojfsCkB0Nh5lPrhQ4kgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=6074ccc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yNNYTbJD1o&amp;t=71s</a><br />\n節奏莊重，氣氛祥和。個人感覺與聖誕節教堂合唱團曲目有幾分相似。歌詞歌頌皇后，對本人乃至香港人都具特別意義。God save our Queen!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6）烏拉圭國歌</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xPI0g4oQcrw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxPI0g4oQcrw&d=GabojfsCkB0Nh5lPrhQ4kgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=994573ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xPI0g4oQcrw</a><br />\n節奏短促，段段緊扣，個人感覺略似歌舞劇曲，十分獨特。歌詞表達人民與祖國的緊密關係，以及烏拉圭人對追求自由的決心。"},{"pid":"e11cd595f4e6d1b9ce0d1ff1e52c95e7691b985d","tid":761074,"uid":52068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:46:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5）澳大利亞國歌</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jbAs616bjmU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjbAs616bjmU&d=GabojfsCkB0Nh5lPrhQ4kgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=e17cb1b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jbAs616bjmU</a><br />\n氣氛柔和、歡樂。特別留意歌詞完全沒有提及戰爭、勝負、生死，只是單純地歌頌國家的豐富資源、絕世美景，簡直是一個與世無爭、自由而又年輕的國度。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4）意大利國歌</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YQ6TdIlDDAg&amp;t=129s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYQ6TdIlDDAg%26t%3D129s&d=GabojfsCkB0Nh5lPrhQ4kgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=268fa193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YQ6TdIlDDAg&amp;t=129s</a><br />\n意大利可謂歐洲文化聚盆，音樂底蘊當然豐厚。歌曲氣氛高昂，令人熱血。歌詞重視意大利民族的偉大，連勝利女神都是他們的奴隸！當中最喜歡的一句：意大利在呼喚！是！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3）巴西國歌</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D4gleaFAWdk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DD4gleaFAWdk&d=GabojfsCkB0Nh5lPrhQ4kgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=76178342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D4gleaFAWdk</a><br />\n節奏輕快，容易令人想像巴西是個充滿活力、和平、歡樂的國家。另外歌詞正面、光明，全曲讚美祖國。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2）俄羅斯國歌</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NyMO-mvl8WI&amp;t=26s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNyMO-mvl8WI%26t%3D26s&d=GabojfsCkB0Nh5lPrhQ4kgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=42f5efe6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NyMO-mvl8WI&amp;t=26s</a><br />\n氣氛宏偉、激昂，令人感受到俄羅斯的強大、紅場的壯觀。另外歌詞讚美祖國，情感祥和。烏拉！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1）法國國歌</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ESFyPlVPREU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DESFyPlVPREU&d=GabojfsCkB0Nh5lPrhQ4kgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=7532d443\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ESFyPlVPREU</a><br />\n馬賽曲，無需多講，實至名歸，無容置疑。"},{"pid":"962d8539c35d8412e47857a2289ebe1cda0deda3","tid":761074,"uid":20449,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:52:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64e12e000c089c3f73d5b03f020cbbcc401e9f64","tid":761074,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:58:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a274ef8dd2bd8d268c71b225d14b3044e665f8e6","tid":761074,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T07:07:32.000Z","msg":"Liebe des vaterlands <br />\nLiebe des freien manns <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84bf736f69156f42da1aa3575007976a382285e4","tid":761074,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T10:50:51.000Z","msg":"德國呢？<br />\n屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=6pkcyAhANvk&amp;t=5s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6pkcyAhANvk%26t%3D5s&d=GabojfsCkB0Nh5lPrhQ4kgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=b641c969\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=6pkcyAhANvk&amp;t=5s</a>"},{"pid":"6115f6f8f21c6cfa20ed71c0ba392bf438809d84","tid":761074,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"962d8539c35d8412e47857a2289ebe1cda0deda3","tid":761074,"uid":20449,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:52:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T10:52:31.000Z","msg":"個、個揸住~<br />\n個兜~"}]}